snippet.title: she dreams elsewhere: "welcome to palm mall" (E3 2021 teaser)
snippet.description:
Welcome to Palm Mall: A place to relax. A place to explore. A place to dream.

Explore this and many other ethereal dreamscapes in SHE DREAMS ELSEWHERE - coming soon to Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S and Nintendo Switch.

WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/492540/She_Dreams_Elsewhere/
WEBSITE & DEV BLOG: https://studiozevere.com/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/studiozevere
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/studiozevere/
DISCORD: https://discord.gg/fwXc3Kq

original music composed by mimi page (@mimipagemusic)
key art by yanina nesterova (@nstrwa)
voiceover by shaila grace (@shailattte)
edited by davionne gooden (@davionnegooden)
